- `./repos/effect/packages/vitest/test/index.test.ts`
- `./repos/effect/packages/vitest/src/index.ts`
- `./repos/effect/packages/vitest/src/internal/internal.ts`
- `./repos/effect/packages/vitest/typetest/index.tst.ts`

